title: STUNNING VIEW IN 1010 BRICKELL!!
posting_body: ['Available now for immediate occupancy!', 'Spectacular unit on the 33rd floor.', 'Enjoy amazing views of the Ocean & Miami city skyline.', '2 bedrooms, 3 full baths, PLUS A DEN with full bathroom, to use as a 3rd guest bedroom or office.', 'Freshly painted with a private elevator entry.', 'The unit comes with upgrades such as modern porcelain floors, LED lights, and motorized shades.', 'The building has incredible amenities, rooftop & indoor pools with bar/grill, spa, fitness center, running track, indoor basketball & squash court, kids water park, and much more.', "Don't miss the opportunity to live in one of the best and highly sought-after buildings in Brickell.", 'Best location!', 'walk to all restaurants and Brickell City Center!', 'all units are one year lease min!', 'credit score close to 700 or higher required, proof of income 2,5 greater than rent price, first month + last month + security deposit to move in!', 'Dilya Taveras', 'Equity Realty', 'TEXT :', 'show contact info']
